full_text:
Fiz o teste no posto, deu positivo para Covid. Teste rápido e gratuito, viva o SUS!
A enfermeira disse que eu ia ser atendido logo na sala ao lado. A sala esta apagada e já deu o horário do almoço, foda-se o SUS! 
Se fosse uma clínica particular ia ser a mesma coisa, viva o SUS!

user.name: 🇲🇿 Ramon Ribeiro 🇦🇴

texto_en:
I took the test at the post, it was positive for covid. quick and free trial, long live sus!
the nurse said that I would be seen right away in the next room. the room is dark and it's time for lunch, fuck sus!
if it was a private clinic it would be the same thing, long live sus!
